    <title>Introduction to CryptoHack部分Write Up</title>
    <url>/2023/01/15/Introduction-to-CryptoHack%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86Write-Up/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>CryptoHack的Introduction to CryptoHack部分Write_Up</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<p>大于等于10分的题不能直接放。。<br>我在研究怎么设置访问限制。。上次试了设密码不知道为什么不成功。。先写几个小于等于10分的题</p>
<h3 id="Finding-Flags"><a href="#Finding-Flags" class="headerlink" title="Finding Flags"></a>Finding Flags</h3><p>CTRL CV</p>
<h3 id="Great-Snakes"><a href="#Great-Snakes" class="headerlink" title="Great Snakes"></a>Great Snakes</h3><p>运行</p>
<h3 id="ASCII"><a href="#ASCII" class="headerlink" title="ASCII"></a>ASCII</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">b= [<span class="number">99</span>, <span class="number">114</span>, <span class="number">121</span>, <span class="number">112</span>, <span class="number">116</span>, <span class="number">111</span>, <span class="number">123</span>, <span class="number">65</span>, <span class="number">83</span>, <span class="number">67</span>, <span class="number">73</span>, <span class="number">73</span>, <span class="number">95</span>, <span class="number">112</span>, <span class="number">114</span>, <span class="number">49</span>, <span class="number">110</span>, <span class="number">116</span>, <span class="number">52</span>, <span class="number">98</span>, <span class="number">108</span>, <span class="number">51</span>, <span class="number">125</span>]</span><br><span class="line">c= [<span class="built_in">chr</span>(d) <span class="keyword">for</span> d <span class="keyword">in</span> b]</span><br><span class="line">a= <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>.join(c)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(a)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#得出结果</span></span><br><span class="line">f=[<span class="built_in">ord</span>(d) <span class="keyword">for</span> d <span class="keyword">in</span> a]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(f)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#反函数运用</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="Hex"><a href="#Hex" class="headerlink" title="Hex"></a>Hex</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a = <span class="string">&#x27;63727970746f7b596f755f77696c6c5f62655f776f726b696e675f776974685f6865785f737472696e67735f615f6c6f747d&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">b = <span class="built_in">bytes</span>.fromhex(a)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span> (b)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#得出结果</span></span><br><span class="line">c = <span class="built_in">bytes</span>.<span class="built_in">hex</span>(b)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(c)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#反函数</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="Base64"><a href="#Base64" class="headerlink" title="Base64"></a>Base64</h3><p>这题居然是编码。。。。好震撼</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> base64</span><br><span class="line">a = <span class="string">&#x27;72bca9b68fc16ac7beeb8f849dca1d8a783e8acf9679bf9269f7bf&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">b = <span class="built_in">bytes</span>.fromhex(a)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span> (b)</span><br><span class="line">c = base64.b64encode(b)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(c)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="Bytes-and-Big-Integers"><a href="#Bytes-and-Big-Integers" class="headerlink" title="Bytes and Big Integers"></a>Bytes and Big Integers</h3><p>我之前装过PyCryptodome，结果差点不知道放在哪里了。。</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> Crypto.Util.number <span class="keyword">import</span> bytes_to_long</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> Crypto.Util.number <span class="keyword">import</span> long_to_bytes</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">a = <span class="number">11515195063862318899931685488813747395775516287289682636499965282714637259206269</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">b = long_to_bytes(a)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(b)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="XOR-Starter0"><a href="#XOR-Starter0" class="headerlink" title="XOR Starter0"></a>XOR Starter0</h3><p>看不懂啊。。。怎么连翻译都看不懂😰。。救救文盲。。救救文盲。。。。。</p>
<p>我捋捋。。。首先。。把字符串每个字符转换成ASCII。。<br>然后逐个和给定数值异或。。？</p>
<p>我捋不明白啊能说中文吗我是文盲啊SOS。。文盲也要读书，文盲也有梦想。。</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a = <span class="string">&#x27;label&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">b = <span class="number">13</span></span><br><span class="line">c = <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> a:</span><br><span class="line">    c += <span class="built_in">chr</span>(<span class="built_in">ord</span>(i) ^ b)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(c)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>文盲做出来了。。文盲真不错。。</p>
<p>好啦接下来的题都是大于十分的。。让我研究一下访问限制。。明天再来。。</p>
]]></content>
